<section id="operationType" role="manufacturing">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>operation types</primary>
      <secondary>creating new</secondary>
    </indexterm>Operation Type</title>
  <para>To create a new operation type, select the <guibutton>NEW</guibutton> button. The following
  screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/operationType.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Create New Operation Type</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When creating a new operation type, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Code</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a unique code to identify the operation type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a description to further identify the operation
        type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
